<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="demand-vt">demand <strong><em>vt</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'mɑːnd/    美 /dɪ'mænd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(坚决) 要求：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Taylor was able to demand very high pay for her movies.  
泰勒能要求很高的片酬。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>demand to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She demanded to see the manager. 
她坚决要求见经理。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>demand + that ... (should) do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Her teachers demanded that she wear longer skirts.
老师要求她穿长些的裙子。</p><footer> 外研⑦ – 6</footer></div>

<p>注: 不能用demand sb to do sth。  </p>
<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>需要：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This work demands care and patience. 
这项工作需要细心和耐心。</p></div></div>